title: Also after Wipe Data the phone is asking for PIN. I put it correctly but it doesn't go forward.
content:
Hello,
I m not able to unlock my Pixel 5 (i put the correct PIN, but nothing).
After a Wipe Data it asks for a PIN again, not allowing me to move over it.
I don't have Debug USB enabled and I can't try any other way via Fastboot or ADB.
